data.description: This 4 bedroom, 2-and-a-half-bathroom home has upgrades everywhere you look. From the high-end light fixtures to the well-designed window coverings the flow of this home is amazing.  Water Softener, reverse osmosis under the kitchen sink, garage is heated and cooled, upgraded spring system on garage door, custom shelving in kitchen, and custom shelving in laundry room. Wow that is a lot, we haven't even mentioned the outside yet!!  Step outside to your private oasis.  Custom one of a kind covered patio that is perfect for your outdoor kitchen, that wait, has a T.V. already installed.  Follow the concrete and well-manicured lawn to the rear of property, sit under the custom pergola and gander at the unobstructed Gatlinburg like view.
